#: src/administration/administration.md:42
msgid "Lemmy-ui"
msgstr ""

#: src/administration/administration.md:44
msgid ""
"Lemmy-ui is the main frontend for Lemmy. It consists of an expressjs based "
"server-side process (necessary for SSR) and client code which run in the "
"browser. It does not use a lot of resources and will happily run on quite "
"low powered servers."
msgstr ""

